room_title: Escape room "Rise of the Zombie Pets" by Brainstorm Escapes: The Conspiratory in Champaign-Urbana
review: It was really fun, even though we missed the mark! We got down to the last puzzle and had a boo boo! We were in the Zombie Room. I will definitely go back if I ever make it back up this way!!!

room_title: Escape room "Rise of the Zombie Pets" by Brainstorm Escapes: The Conspiratory in Champaign-Urbana
review: We had a great time completing the very challenging Zombie Pet room (in the nick of time)! Would definitely recommend the experience to anyone

room_title: Escape room "Rise of the Zombie Pets" by Brainstorm Escapes: The Conspiratory in Champaign-Urbana
review: Had a great time as part of a team building event with my company. I was in the Zombie Room which was pretty awesome. We escaped with about 2 minutes left on the clock. Staff is great and I can't wait to come back next year for another adventure.

room_title: Escape room "Rise of the Zombie Pets" by Brainstorm Escapes: The Conspiratory in Champaign-Urbana
review: Brought a crowd from work to the Zombie Pet room. Excellent. Learned a lot about each other's skill sets and strengths. The host was very engaged during and after our room. He spent a long time identifying what roles people fell into.

room_title: Escape room "Rise of the Zombie Pets" by Brainstorm Escapes: The Conspiratory in Champaign-Urbana
review: Had so much fun even though we failed and became zombies lmao. Will definitely be doing this again.
